{
  "stem": "22869.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from there on, they shipped them to either Auschwitz or any other camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we had-- we had, as a matter of fact, in the-- when the occupation of Poland happened, we had several times a-- a few men who ran away from Poland.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one of them, I remember-- I can't remember his name-- but I remember clearly that he walked for weeks over the fields, hiding.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by the time he arrived in our city, he had no teeth, because he-- he-- he was like on-- like on a-- a starvation time, eating just what he found in the fields, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By the time he arrived, he had almost no teeth left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember we took him into our home for-- for a period of time, and-- and I can't recall exactly later on what happened with that person.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But to the best of my knowledge, I think he was deported with the rest of us from Slovakia to concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you have to remember that, at that time, the only thing that would happen was that there was mass shootings, mass killings.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no-- there was no such a thing as-- as-- he did not know any information about-- that he could give us, so we would know, wait a minute, be cautious, because you're going to fall into the same trap.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was all just that-- that there is-- the Germans are mean to the Jewish people, that they're killing them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they're-- they don't take any kind of exception if it's a man, woman, child, old people, young people, so forth.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
